scene.message:
Takeda: Who are you?!{nl}
Children again?!{nl}
How did you get in?!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: Pathetic, Takeda.{nl}
After that last boy,{nl}
when did we become a daycare?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Same as ever, Kandori.{nl}
For a fox borrowing a{nl}
tiger's authority,{waitkey}{clearbox}you're taking things{nl}
rather far, aren't you?{nl}
Does Chairman Saeki know{nl}
about this?{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: Well, well —{nl}
the Nanjo Konzern's{nl}
young master.{waitkey}{clearbox}The old man knows nothing.{nl}
And by the way —{nl}
sneaking around like a thief{nl}
will get you spanked.{waitkey}{nl}
By your senile butler,{nl}
perhaps?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Silence!{nl}
You... you alone{nl}
I'll never forgive!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, pal!{nl}
Don't look so smug —{nl}
you're gonna answer for this!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Just as expected.{nl}
The arrogance — a villain{nl}
really needs this quality.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: He looks weaker{nl}
than I expected!{nl}
{ctl08:65281}I'll handle that big one!{waitkey}{clearbox}After all, the leader{nl}
should take on the boss!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, old man!{nl}
Don't treat us like kids!{nl}
And what's with the ball?!{waitkey}Such an old man thing!{nl}
Wrinkle face!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: ...{wait_fr:80}{nl}
Undisciplined brats{nl}
are the same as beasts.{waitkey}{clearbox}Takeda — kill them.{nl}
Try not to make a mess{nl}
of the room.{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Takeda.{nl}
Kandori's right-hand man.{nl}
Handles SEBEC's{nl}
illegal operations.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Kandori Takahisa.{nl}
Ambitious branch manager{nl}
of SEBEC. Dark rumors{nl}
follow him always.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: No sign he used{nl}
the door. There must{nl}
be another exit.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: ...So that's{nl}
Kandori...{nl}
I feel like I've seen him...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Are you alright, Maki?{nl}
You look a little{nl}
pale.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hmm?{nl}
What's wrong, Maki?{nl}
You look really serious.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hmm?{nl}
What's wrong, Sonoda?{nl}
You look down.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Huh? Oh... I'm fine.{nl}
I'm okay, really.{nl}
Come on, let's catch him!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: There must be another{nl}
exit. I'll watch outside —{nl}
find it quickly.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: They can use{nl}
Personas — that was{nl}
a surprise.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Really, I'm fine.{nl}
Just a little dizzy, that's{nl}
all. Sorry to worry you.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Kandori's Persona...{nl}
The faceless god...{nl}
the crawling chaos...{waitkey}A deity of countless names{nl}
and twisted form. A symbol{nl}
of malice itself.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Get it together —{nl}
he got away!{waitkey}{ret}

There's a switch.{nl}
Press it?{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Nanjo: A hidden passage.{nl}
What a petty little{nl}
man he is.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {ctl07:1},{nl}
are you uninjured?{nl}
Shall we go?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: He's the one who{nl}
messed up our town...{nl}
I'll never forgive him!{waitkey}{clearbox}Huh...? Aha, nothing!{nl}
Let's go!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Ahead, I'm sure,{nl}
lies the sorry shape{nl}
of his petty ambitions.{waitkey}{ret}
